// English content -------------------
$title[0] 	= "Rank: Recruit";
$banner[0] 	= "<img src=\"../images/banner_recruit.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />";
$rnk_p11[0]	= "The rank of recruit identifies an entry level student of the martial art known as <b><i>l`arte dell`armizare</i></b> or simply as <b><i>armizare</i></b>. A newly registered student who first begins their training at AEMMA, they are informed with an overview of the Academy, the key personnel, and given an overview of the training program, its structure and duration. The <b>recruit</b> then begins with receiving instruction on the foundations of abrazare (grappling), daga (dagger) and spada (swordplay) based on the <a href=\"mo_about_schedule.php\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse the training schedule\">training schedule</a>.";
$rnk_p12[0]	= "As a new <b>recruit</b>, the student is entitled the opportunity to assess whether or not to pursue this form of martial art with a level commitment which is compatible with their current life style and commitments. During this trial period, recruit training equipment requirements to begin training incurs a modest cost which encompasses the purchase of an AEMMA training t-shirt, leather garden-variety gloves, black training leggings/slacks and comfortable flat-soled running shoes (some of which may already be in possession of the new student). ";
$rnk_p13[0]	= "After a period of training, which can take from 8 months to 2 or more years, the recruit may be ready to challenge for the rank of <a href=\"mo_rnk_scholler.php\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse the rank of scholler information\">scholler</a>. At this point of recruit training, the student should not consider him/herself a fighter just yet, however, he/she will possess the necessary foundational skills to build upon and to develop those skills into sophisticated fighting techniques in the <a href=\"mo_rnk_scholler.php\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse the rank of scholler information\">scholler</a> level of training, and will be able to deploy some basic defensive maneuvres if required if an opportunity presents itself. Upon completing the recruit training, the program is designed so that the student is then in a position and prepared to challenge for the prize of <a href=\"mo_rnk_scholler.php\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse the rank of scholler information\">scholler</a> by undergoing a public <a href=\"\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse a sample scholler test\">scholler test</a> in the presence of the student's peers. Of course, at this point in the recruit's training, other compulsory <a href=\"\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse details on the scholler training equipment\">scholler training equipment</a> would have been purchased, as this is another requirement for challenging for the <a href=\"mo_rnk_scholler.php\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse the rank of scholler information\">scholler</a> rank. ";

$title_p2[0] 	= "Recruit Requirements";
$rnk_l21[0]	= "no previous martial arts training experience necessary,";
$rnk_l22[0]	= "must be 18 years or more <i>(applicants younger than 18 must be accompanied by a guardian for signing the relevant forms, and is interviewed by the instructor(s) to determine if the applicant is mature enough to train)</i>,";
$rnk_l23[0]	= "completed administrative forms which includes the membership application and individual waiver form provided by one of the officers,";
$rnk_l24[0]	= "the application has been approved and accepted by the Academy,";
$rnk_l25[0]	= "a photo of the recruit taken by a member of AEMMA, or transmitted to AEMMA in jpg/png format, for inclusion of the recruit's training record in the AEMMA membership training database (used internally by instructors only),";
$rnk_l26[0]	= "<a href=\"mo_about_fees.php\" title=\"click to peruse the training fees details\" target=\"_top\">training fees</a> are paid for on a regular basis and there are no outstanding dues,";
$rnk_l27[0]	= "click ==> <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse recruit equipment requirements\" target=\"_top\">equipment requirements</a> for details and descriptions on minimum recruit equipment requirements,";
$rnk_l28[0]	= "the recruit has read, understand and conforms to the <a href=\"mo_about_rules.php\" title=\"click to peruse the Rules of the Salle\" target=\"_top\">Rules of the Salle d'Armes</a>.";

$title_p3[0] 	= "Recruit Study and Activities Expectations";
$rnk_p3[0] 	= "The following are further details of the recruit training program, requirements and expectations. These must be fully developed before challenging for the prize of <a href=\"mo_rnk_scholler.php\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse the rank of scholler information\">scholler</a>. Typically, the AEMMA instructors will know if a recruit is ready to challenge for the prize of <a href=\"mo_rnk_scholler.php\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse the rank of scholler information\">scholler</a> and will discuss this possibility with the recruit to determine if the recruit him/herself is prepared to go the extra yard to prepare oneself for the prize of the rank of <a href=\"mo_rnk_scholler.php\" target=\"_top\" title=\"click to peruse the rank of scholler information\">scholler</a>.";
$rnk_l31[0]	= "read and study the following recommended historical manuscripts that are available online: Fiore dei Liberi's <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse Flos Duellatorum\" target=\"_top\">Flos Duellatorum</a> and George Silver's <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse Paradoxes of Defense\" target=\"_top\">Paradoxes of Defense</a> and <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse Brief Instructions on my Paradoxes of Defense\" target=\"_top\">Brief Instructions on my Paradoxes of Defense</a>,";
$rnk_l32[0]	= "recruits are encouraged to practice the drills outside (homework) the formal training session of the Academy,";
$rnk_l33[0]	= "recruits are encouraged to engage in additional conditioning and strength training to help develop their strength and endurance,";
$rnk_l34[0]	= "recruits are encouraged to attend as a representative of Academy or chapter at symposiums, workshops and conferences at a reduced fee,";
$rnk_l35[0]	= "recruits are encouraged to volunteer and assist in the general operational and administrative activities of the Academy (workshop coordination and setup, equipment administration, demonstrations, etc.),";
$rnk_l36[0]	= "if the recruit is serious about pursuing this training beyond recruit, he/she is encouraged to acquire the relevant <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse scholler-oriented equipment requirements\" target=\"_top\">scholler-oriented equipment</a> in preparation for his/her future scholar test.";

$title_p4[0] 	= "Skills Development and Training Expectations for the Recruit";
$rnk_l4a[0] 	= "<b>Theory</b>";
$rnk_l41[0]	= "combative theory, concepts and history including a familiarity and understanding of George Silver's fighting concepts (e.g. true times, false times, governors) as described in <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse Brief Instructions on my Paradoxes of Defense\" target=\"_top\">Brief Instructions on my Paradoxes of Defense</a>,";
$rnk_l42[0]	= "the structure, nomenclature and physics of the sword,";
$rnk_l43[0]	= "some familiarity with the various <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse armour components\" target=\"_top\">armour components</a>,";
$rnk_l44[0]	= "familiarity with the English nomenclature of the poste and their equivalents in Friulian terms,";
$rnk_l45[0]	= "a familiarity with Fiore dei Liberi's treatises <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse Flos Duellatorum\" target=\"_top\">Flos Duellatorum and Fior di Battaglia</a>, the versions of Fiore's treatises known, the differences and similarities between the versions, background of Fiore dei Liberi, familiarity with the prologue of the treatises, and its relationship to the training received,";
$rnk_l46[0]	= "the recruit understands the mission of AEMMA.";
$rnk_l4b[0] 	= "<b>Technical</b>";
$rnk_l51[0]	= "foundations in <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse abrazare or grappling techniques\" target=\"_top\"><i>abrazare</i> or grappling techniques</a>,";
$rnk_l52[0]	= "foundations in <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse daga or dagger techniques\" target=\"_top\"><i>daga</i> or dagger techniques</a> - attacks, counters, evading, disarms, etc.";
$rnk_l53[0]	= "foundations in <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse spada or arming sword techniques\" target=\"_top\"><i>spada</i> or arming sword techniques</a>,";
$rnk_l54[0]	= "develop skills in the classic guards (<i>poste</i>) and strikes,";
$rnk_l55[0]	= "develop skills in basic parrying/re-direction techniques,";
$rnk_l56[0]	= "develop skills in entries and disarms.";
$rnk_l57[0]	= "a basic understanding and demonstration of footwork, including passing, <i>traverse, volta, volta stabile, meza volta</i>, and gather steps,";
$rnk_l58[0]	= "the ability to deliver all of the drills trained in this skill level both from an individual perspective and in pairs.";

$title_p6[0] 	= "Other Recruit Attributes:";
$rnk_l61[0]	= "cross-training techniques are often introduced through Jeet Kune Do (JKD) to enhance training in sensitivity, including <a href=\"\" title=\"click to peruse fundamental holds and throws\" target=\"_top\">fundamental holds and throws</a> (in preparation for abrazare & daga techniques later),";
$rnk_l62[0]	= "exhibits control and discipline during training, drills and free-fencing bouts,";
$rnk_l63[0]	= "exposure to cutting with the longsword or arming sword using a sharpened steel sword,";
$rnk_l64[0]	= "estimate completion of this level of training is a 8-24 month period depending upon frequency of attending practices, and previous martial arts experience.";

?>
